init_text:
Are We Being Bad Citizens If We Don't Keep Up With the News?

In your opinion, are we being bad citizens if we don't keep up with the news? Do you think all people have some responsibility to know what is going on in the world? Does engaging with current events actually do anything at all? Why do you think the way you do?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think that we should at least have an idea of what's going on in the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I remember growing up in a small town in Idaho and there was one news station so it was always just the same story over and over again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There were no other sources of information and the news station only talked about local events.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think for people who lived in smaller towns or grew up in the 90s, there was not access to news.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As technology became more advanced and phones and laptops were invented, it became easier to access the information from all around the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In this day and age, it is pretty hard to be disconnected from the internet.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: With social media apps and news stories being shared all the time, it is hard to not be aware of certain things that are going on in the world

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: I think for people who lived in smaller towns or grew up in the 90s, there was not access to news.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, I think it's important to be conscious of the news that you pay attention to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is extremely complex and you can't be aware of everything.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's important to know how and why news is framed, who makes money off of it, and what is the truth behind each story.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The news is one of the many tools society has to make progress.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: The news is one of the many tools society has to make progress.
